images.caption: Minnesota Lynx' Alanna Smith and Myisha Hines-Allen celebrate after winning Game 1 of the 2024 WNBA Finals.

images.name: Lynx overcome 18-point deficit to steal Game 1 from Liberty
images.caption: The Lynx mount a remarkable comeback to wipe away an 18-point deficit and take Game 1 of the WNBA Finals from the Liberty.

articles.description: Napheesa Collier's turnaround jumper with 8.8 seconds remaining secured a 95-93 victory for the Minnesota Lynx over the New York Liberty in Game 1 of the 2024 WNBA Finals.
articles.headline: Lynx's comeback in WNBA Finals G1 win over Liberty sends social media into overdrive
